# Technology Stack & Versions

Complete reference for all major dependencies, versions, and best practices for the Complytude Backend.

## Core Framework

### NestJS v11.0.1

**Components:**

- `@nestjs/core`: ^11.0.1
- `@nestjs/common`: ^11.0.1
- `@nestjs/cli`: ^11.0.0 (dev)
- `@nestjs/schematics`: ^11.0.0 (dev)

**Best Practices:**

- NestJS 11 is the latest major version with improved performance and TypeScript 5.7 support
- Use dependency injection consistently across all modules
- Follow modular architecture with clear module boundaries
- Leverage decorators for metadata and configuration
- Use the latest lifecycle hooks and interceptors

**Version Notes:**

- NestJS 11 requires Node.js 18.x or higher (project uses 22.16.0+)
- Breaking changes from v10: Updated to support TypeScript 5.x strict mode
- Enhanced support for Fastify v5

